              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "LKk1s",
                  "name": "Frame 1",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "5R0To",
                      "name": "dr1N",
                      "fill": "#888888",
                      "content": "01",
                      "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "eTG0R",
                      "name": "dr1R",
                      "width": 636,
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "dwC9e",
                          "name": "dr1T",
                          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                          "content": "Strategic Intelligence",
                          "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "WwMEE",
                          "name": "dr1D",
                          "fill": "#666666",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "We translate complexity into clear, actionable decision frameworks by breaking down intricate problems into structured, comprehensible layers that leadership teams can confidently engage with. Instead of overwhelming stakeholders with fragmented data or abstract insights, we synthesize information into cohesive analyses that reveal patterns, dependencies, risks, and opportunities in a way that is both strategic and practical. Our approach ensures that every critical variable is examined, every assumption is challenged, and every possible outcome is considered, enabling decision-makers to see the full picture with clarity and precision. This structured perspective empowers organizations to move forward with confidence, allocate resources more effectively, minimize uncertainty, and make informed commitments that are grounded in deep understanding rather than guesswork or intuition alone.\n",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "j1ika",
                  "fill": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "enabled": true,
                    "url": "startae-team-7tXA8xwe4W4-unsplash.jpg",
                    "mode": "fill"
                  },
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": "fill_container"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "AIDJb",
              "name": "dr2",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": "fill_container",
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#F3F4F6"
              },
              "gap": 80,
              "padding": 80,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "iG5ff",
                  "fill": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "enabled": true,
                    "url": "Gemini_Generated_Image_3l6aso3l6aso3l6a.png",
                    "mode": "fill"
                  },
                  "width": 566,
                  "height": "fill_container"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "8bfw5",
                  "name": "Frame 3",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "V5q7a",
                      "name": "dr2N",
                      "fill": "#888888",
                      "content": "02",
                      "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "Knp63",
                      "name": "dr2R",
                      "width": 634,
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "65bHs",
                          "name": "dr2T",
                          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                          "content": "AI Integration",
                          "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "w05cF",
                          "name": "dr2D",
                          "fill": "#666666",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "We embed AI directly into decision-making processes—not as a superficial add-on or a trend-driven gimmick, but as a genuine force multiplier for structured thinking. Instead of treating AI as a black box that produces isolated outputs, we integrate it into the core analytical workflow, where it augments human judgment by accelerating pattern recognition, stress-testing assumptions, and surfacing insights that might otherwise remain hidden. This allows teams to move beyond intuition-led decisions and toward a more disciplined, evidence-backed approach, where complexity is not just managed but actively leveraged. By combining computational intelligence with clear frameworks and human context, we enable faster, sharper, and more resilient decisions—ensuring that leadership operates with both speed and depth, rather than having to trade one for the other.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "FmzJj",
              "name": "dr3",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": "fill_container",
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#F3F4F6"
              },
              "gap": 80,
              "padding": 80,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "vJDzA",
                  "name": "Frame 4",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "hQE2A",
                      "name": "dr3N",
                      "fill": "#888888",
                      "content": "03",
                      "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "EQezk",
                      "name": "dr3R",
                      "width": 634,
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "cETqd",
                          "name": "dr3T",
                          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                          "content": "Decision Architecture",
                          "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "AlNC0",
                          "name": "dr3D",
                          "fill": "#666666",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Designing systems and processes that enable consistently better decisions requires more than isolated improvements—it demands a deliberate, end-to-end approach that aligns governance, workflows, and accountability into a cohesive structure. From defining robust governance frameworks that establish clear decision rights, guardrails, and escalation paths, to crafting intuitive workflows that reduce friction and guide teams toward the right actions, every layer is intentionally designed to reinforce clarity and consistency. The focus is not just on making individual decisions better, but on building an environment where good decisions become the default outcome over time. By embedding structure into how information flows, how trade-offs are evaluated, and how outcomes are measured, organizations can eliminate ambiguity, reduce dependency on individual judgment, and create repeatable systems that scale—ensuring that decision quality improves not sporadically, but systematically.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "50UG4",
